race.comment: STARRY RAYMAR (6) was in traffic close to the inside last time over 380m at this track and fell. Key player on best form and expected to bounce back. BINDI BOODIE (3) slotted in just off the lead from the wide draw last start and boxed on to finish second (22.05) at this track in a Grade 6 over 380m. Can measure up. PANADOM (1) turned spotting a big start finishing eighth (22.80) last time in a Grade 6 at this track. Has ability and is one of the better chances. CASH MANAGER (2) with some luck can improve on an unplaced run last time here.
